Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class Turn

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.Turn
public class Turn
extends java.lang.Object
The class representing a turn of the game, during which a worker can move, build a block, force or build a dome
